rows.label: qst202401_msg0001
rows.name:
Meh meh!
You bring Tirkin here?

rows.label: qst202401_msg0002
rows.name: How dare show face around here!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0004
rows.name:
Don't play dummy-dumb with
Noganga! You in big trouble!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0005
rows.name:
What?
Do you think Ibuki is a Tirkin?

rows.label: qst202401_msg0006
rows.name: ...She not?

rows.label: qst202401_msg0007
rows.name:
No way!
A Tirkin? Me?
I'm a Blade!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0008
rows.name:
If that true then why you
not say earlier?

rows.label: qst202401_msg0009
rows.name:
Look too similar to Tirkin so probably
everybody confused all the time!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0010
rows.name:
You're the one who jumped
to conclusions, pal!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0011
rows.name:
What do you have against
Tirkin, anyway?

rows.label: qst202401_msg0012
rows.name: Glad you asked!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0013
rows.name:
It all start when Noganga come back
home after negotiating in Gula.

rows.label: qst202401_msg0014
rows.name:
Divine Beast ship was attacked by Tirkin
and Noganga's precious Nopon
Trade Guild ID was stolen!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0015
rows.name:
Now to do trading, Noganga must
wade through many red tapes
and bureaucratic nonsense.

rows.label: qst202401_msg0016
rows.name: Tirkin take anything that shiny!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0017
rows.name:
And so birdbrain that they immediately
forget where they hide things!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0018
rows.name:
It all Tirkin's fault that Noganga
cannot trade easily any more!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0019
rows.name:
So you understand why sight of
Tirkin lookalike make Noganga angry!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0020
rows.name: Are you done venting?

rows.label: qst202401_msg0036
rows.name: Hey, Boppi, did you hear?

rows.label: qst202401_msg0037
rows.name:
Fishy Fishy are having a half-price
sale on fish paste. Let's go
shopping there later!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0038
rows.name:
Bargain is good! Leave it to Hana
to carry all shopping bags!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0039
rows.name: Ibuki! Are you even listening?

rows.label: qst202401_msg0040
rows.name: Uhh, what were we talking about again?

rows.label: qst202401_msg0041
rows.name:
Noganga was just saying how
much you look like a Tirkin.

rows.label: qst202401_msg0021
rows.name:
Oh yeah, I remember now! Well I have
no idea what he's talking about.

rows.label: qst202401_msg0022
rows.name:
What part of me is supposed
to look like a Tirkin, exactly?
I couldn't be more different!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0023
rows.name:
No no! No matter which way you
slice it, you exactly Tirkin!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0024
rows.name: And inside head is birdbrain too!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0025
rows.name: Nuh-uh! Is not!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0026
rows.name:
Hehe. If you better in brains than
stupid Tirkin, prove it!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0027
rows.name:
With pleasure! You know what,
I'm gonna go get back your dumb
Nopon Trade Guild ID!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0028
rows.name:
If I manage it, that's gotta be proof
that I'm smarter than a Tirkin, right?

rows.label: qst202401_msg0029
rows.name:
Ibuki...
Why do I get the feeling you played
right into his hands there?

rows.label: qst202401_msg0030
rows.name:
I-it'sokay! Doesn't matter!
It's all good!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0031
rows.name:
So where was this whatever
thingummy ID stolen?

rows.label: qst202401_msg0032
rows.name:
We were attacked while passing by
Liberalitan Archipelago.

rows.label: qst202401_msg0033
rows.name:
Tirkin lair definitely around
there somewhere!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0034
rows.name:
If you bring back Noganga's ID,
it proof you smarter than Tirkin!

rows.label: qst202401_msg0035
rows.name: Okay! Let's do this, people!
